Name: BringIT to MOM
About the game: When MOM needs help, transform yourself and go on a journey. Begin ILL’s adventure. Help MOM to recover and save your planet. Find out two endings of the story. Go through 50 different escape rooms. Use a rope, roll, jump, fly, dive, bounce, collect galaxies and energy. MOM needs more energy. Bring it to her. What’s waiting for you: – an interesting adventure and arcade game scenario, – 2 different endings, – 50 levels, – surprising extra escape rooms, – great fun for hours, – an ending that you agree with?!
